  <brief_title>Vitamin C as an Adjunct in Periodontal Treatment in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Vitamin C as an Adjunct in Periodontal Treatment in Uncontrolled Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
