  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Periodontitis patients with uncontrolled type 2 diabetes mellitus will receive non-surgical
      periodontal treatment and then be supplemented with daily 500 mg vitamin C (test group) or
      placebo (control group) for 2 months. Clinical parameters will be retrieved at baseline, at
      the end of week 4 and at the end of week 8.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
